@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uhwlqf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.51 * tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.74)) + v1)
    v2 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.48 - v0 + 0.90) / (v1 + 0.45 * v0 + 0.69)))
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.exp(v0) + v0)
    v2 = (v0 - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.96) * 0.28))
    data[tid] = v0
